               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Ṣalota kidān za-śalastu gizeyāt “Covenant Prayer of the Three Hours”
                     (fols. 3r-16r)
 II) Excerpt from the Ordinary of the Mass (fols. 16r-26v)
                     (Śǝrʿāta Qǝddāse III, §§ 56-98), cp. QMA-005
 III) Tǝmhǝrta ḫǝbuʾāt
                     “Teaching of the Mysteries” (fols. 27r-37v)
 IV) ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer za-bǝrhānāt
                     ʾǝgziʾabǝḥer za-śǝlṭānāt… “God of Lights, God of Powers…” (fols. 38r-43r)
                     V) Anaphora of Our Lord Jesus Christ (fols. 43r-53r)
 
 Additio
                     1.</summary>
