                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; two groups of lines on the incipit
                           page of Text I; first two lines on the incipit page of Texts III and IV;
                           initial words of sections in Texts II and V; initial words of subsections
                           in Text III; abbreviations (ይ)ካ፡, (ይ)ሕ፡, (ይ)ዲ፡, ቡ (s. Abbreviations), the
                           word በእንተ፡ and its abbreviations; elements of the punctuation signs and
                           of the Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1"> <locus target="#53v">f. 53v</locus>
                           <desc>: Ownership note. </desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez"> <locus target="#53v">53v</locus>: ፲፱፻፵፱ ዝመጽኀፍ፡
                              የመምሬ፡ ቢያበይን፡ መጽኀፍ፡ ነው፡ ፲፱፻፴፮ዓመተ፡ ምህራት፡.</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The note is written in Gǝʿǝz and Amharic in strong rose pen. It
                              mentions mämǝre Biyabäyyǝn as the owner of the Ms. and it is dated to
                              1949 or 1936 year of mercy. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Text II contains musical notation signs inserted
                           interlineally. 
 - Omitted letters inserted interlineally, <locus target="#26r">26r-</locus>v; in red ink, <locus target="#25r">25r</locus>.
 - Omitted words written in the upper margin in
                           black ink: <locus target="#28v">28v</locus>, 36r-v, 37r.
 -
                           (Omitted?) letters or words inserted interlineally in a secondary hand in
                           blue pen: <locus target="#6r">6r-</locus>v, 7r, 8r, 10v.
 - Erasures:
                              <locus target="#6r">6r</locus>, 21r.
 - Corrections written over
                           erasures: <locus target="#6r">6r</locus>, 9r, 11v.
 - Immediate
                           corrections indicated by dashes above and below the letter, fol 26r, or
                           by a frame, <locus target="#49r">49r</locus>.
 - Spaces for
                           rubrication left unfilled: <locus target="#3r">3r</locus>, 17r.
 -
                           Erased names: <locus target="#41r">41r-</locus>v, 42r, 43r.
 - Pen
                           trial: <locus target="#1r">1r</locus>, 53v.
 - Scribbles: e.g.,
                              <locus target="#1v">1v</locus>, 2r, 2v, 3r, 8v, 13v.
 - A note in
                           black ink has been effaced on <locus target="#37v">37v</locus>.
 -
                           Traces of glue on <locus target="#2v">2v</locus>, possibly due to the
                           former presence of an image.
 - The name of the Metropolitan is
                           indicated by the word ʿǝgäle on <locus target="#19v">19v</locus> and 21r
                           (here erased).</item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
